Package: bustt
Type: Package
Title: Bus and transit time and headways for GTFS
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Tom Buckley <tom@tbuckl.com> [aut,cre]",
    "Kearey Smith [ctb]",
    "Dave Vautin [ctb]"
  ))
Description: Calculate headways and work with time and schedules for bus, train, etc on GTFS data. Answer questions like: 
  What are the headway of train lines at 59-Street Columbus Circle on Saturdays?
  What are the typical headway characteristics of the A Train on weekdays?
License: GPL
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 3.2.4)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    lubridate,
    tidyr,
    rlang
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/r-gtfs/bustt
BugReports: https://github.com/r-gtfs/bustt/issues
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
